Recommends: poppler-utils,
            podman | docker.io,
            gnome-keyring | kwalletmanager
Description: Fast Linux file content search with tabs, replace, and AI assistance
 Grexa is a daily-driver developer utility. It performs grep / ripgrep-style
 searches with a polished Qt 6 / Kirigami interface, atomic-rename safe
 replace, OOXML/ODF/PDF document extraction, Docker + Podman container
 search, optional AI assistance, and a fully scriptable CLI.

Package: grexa-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: poppler-utils
Description: Headless command-line companion to Grexa
 Provides `grexa-cli`, the same search engine without the Qt GUI. Useful
 for scripting, CI integrations, and use over SSH.
